markdown: ITC Limited REPORT AND ACCOUNTS 2013 Personal Care Products W ESSENZA DI WILLS YOUR ESSENCE YOUR SOUL Essenza Di Wills personifies innate style with its exclusive range of fine fragrances and personal care products. The brand unites distinct craftsmanship and passion and is an embodiment of fine living. <::A collection of cosmetic or fragrance products is displayed. The items include various bottles, tubes, and boxes, predominantly in black, white, silver, and clear glass. Many products feature the brand name "ESSENZA DI WILLS". Specifically, there are: - A black cylindrical spray bottle and a taller silver cylindrical spray bottle. - Several rectangular and square glass bottles, some clear with "AQUA" visible, and others opaque. - A white tube labeled "AQUA". - A black spherical bottle. - A black rectangular box or card with an image of a woman and "ESSENZA DI WILLS". - Several white bar soaps, some with "ESSENZA DI WILLS" embossed. - Various product boxes, some black and some white, also bearing the "ESSENZA DI WILLS" branding. : figure::> <::A black and white image features a woman on the left side, looking directly at the viewer. Her hair is dark and styled, and she has a serious expression. On the right side, against a dark gray background, is the "fiama DI WILLS" logo, which consists of a geometric pattern above the word "fiama" and "DI WILLS" below it. To the right of the logo, there is text that reads: "Fiama Di Wills offers a range of expert solutions designed to make consumers look & feel young. With innovation at its core, Fiama Di Wills offers an enviable portfolio of products developed through years of scientific research at Laboratoire Naturel." Below this text and extending across the bottom right of the image is a collection of various Fiama Di Wills cosmetic products, including bottles of shampoo, conditioner, shower gel, bars of soap, and other skincare items, all arranged in a display. The woman's shoulder and arm are visible in the foreground, partially obscuring some of the products on the left.: image::> Source: https://www.industrydocuments.ucsf.edu/docs/snbx0223
